{"tha-ap553:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap553:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap553:0.3":"Yasattheraapadana ","tha-ap553:1.1":"“Mahasamuddam oggayha, ","tha-ap553:1.2":"bhavanam me sunimmitam; ","tha-ap553:1.3":"Sunimmita pokkharani, ","tha-ap553:1.4":"cakkavakupakujita. ","tha-ap553:2.1":"Mandarakehi sanchanna, ","tha-ap553:2.2":"padumuppalakehi ca; ","tha-ap553:2.3":"Nadi ca sandate tattha, ","tha-ap553:2.4":"supatittha manorama. ","tha-ap553:3.1":"Macchakacchapasanchanna, ","tha-ap553:3.2":"nanadijasamotthata; ","tha-ap553:3.3":"Mayurakoncabhiruda, ","tha-ap553:3.4":"kokiladihi vagguhi. ","tha-ap553:4.1":"Parevata ravihamsa, ","tha-ap553:4.2":"cakkavaka nadicara; ","tha-ap553:4.3":"Tittira salika cettha, ","tha-ap553:4.4":"pavaka jivamjivaka. ","tha-ap553:5.1":"Hamsakoncabhinadita, ","tha-ap553:5.2":"kosiya pingala bahu; ","tha-ap553:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap553:5.4":"manimuttapavalika. ","tha-ap553:6.1":"Sabbe sonnamaya rukkha, ","tha-ap553:6.2":"nanakhandhasamerita; ","tha-ap553:6.3":"Ujjotenti divarattim, ","tha-ap553:6.4":"bhavanam sabbakalikam. ","tha-ap553:7.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap553:7.2":"sayam pato pavajjare; ","tha-ap553:7.3":"Solasitthisahassani, ","tha-ap553:7.4":"parivarenti mam sada. ","tha-ap553:8.1":"Abhinikkhamma bhavana, ","tha-ap553:8.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap553:8.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap553:8.4":"vandayim tam mahayasam. ","tha-ap553:9.1":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap553:9.2":"sasangham tam nimantayim; ","tha-ap553:9.3":"Adhivasesi so dhiro, ","tha-ap553:9.4":"sumedho lokanayako. ","tha-ap553:10.1":"Mama dhammakatham katva, ","tha-ap553:10.2":"uyyojesi mahamuni; ","tha-ap553:10.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap553:10.4":"bhavanam me upagamim. ","tha-ap553:11.1":"Amantayim parijanam, ","tha-ap553:11.2":"sabbe sannipatum tada; ","tha-ap553:11.3":"‘Pubbanhasamayam buddho, ","tha-ap553:11.4":"bhavanam agamissati. ","tha-ap553:12.1":"Labha amham suladdha no, ","tha-ap553:12.2":"ye vasama tavantike; ","tha-ap553:12.3":"Mayampi buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap553:12.4":"pujayissama satthuno’. ","tha-ap553:13.1":"Annam panam patthapetva, ","tha-ap553:13.2":"kalam arocayim aham; ","tha-ap553:13.3":"Vasisatasahassehi, ","tha-ap553:13.4":"upesi lokanayako. ","tha-ap553:14.1":"Pancangikehi turiyehi, ","tha-ap553:14.2":"paccuggamamakasaham; ","tha-ap553:14.3":"Sabbasonnamaye pithe, ","tha-ap553:14.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap553:15.1":"Uparicchadanam asi, ","tha-ap553:15.2":"sabbasonnamayam tada; ","tha-ap553:15.3":"Bijaniyo pavayanti, ","tha-ap553:15.4":"bhikkhusangham anuttaram. ","tha-ap553:16.1":"Pahutenannapanena, ","tha-ap553:16.2":"bhikkhusangham atappayim; ","tha-ap553:16.3":"Paccekadussayugale, ","tha-ap553:16.4":"bhikkhusanghassadasaham. ","tha-ap553:17.1":"Yam vadeti sumedho so, ","tha-ap553:17.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap553:17.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap553:17.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap553:18.1":"‘Yo mam annena panena, ","tha-ap553:18.2":"sabbe ime ca tappayi; ","tha-ap553:18.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap553:18.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap553:19.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap553:19.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap553:19.3":"Sahassakkhattum rajayam, ","tha-ap553:19.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap553:20.1":"Upagacchati yam yonim, ","tha-ap553:20.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap553:20.3":"Sabbasonnamayam tassa, ","tha-ap553:20.4":"chadanam dharayissati. ","tha-ap553:21.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap553:21.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap553:21.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap553:21.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap553:22.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap553:22.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap553:22.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap553:22.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap553:23.1":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap553:23.2":"sihanadam nadissati; ","tha-ap553:23.3":"Citake chattam dharenti, ","tha-ap553:23.4":"hettha chattamhi dayhatha’. ","tha-ap553:24.1":"Samannam me anuppattam, ","tha-ap553:24.2":"kilesa jhapita maya; ","tha-ap553:24.3":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","tha-ap553:24.4":"santaso me na vijjati. ","tha-ap553:25.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap553:25.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap553:25.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap553:25.4":"sabbadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap553:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap553:26.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap553:26.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap553:26.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap553:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap553:27.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap553:27.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap553:27.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap553:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap553:28.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap553:28.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap553:28.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap553:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma yaso thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap553:30.1":"Yasattherassapadanam pathamam. "}